Package com.github.maxopoly.angeliacore.model.block

Class ChunkHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.maxopoly.angeliacore.model.block.ChunkHolder
  • public class ChunkHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds all chunks, which contain all block data. For performance reasons holding block data can be disabled via the global config. If any methods are called while no block data is held, a BlockModelNotHeldException will be thrown
